category: Devel Libs
requires: cygwin libosinfo1.0_0
external-source: libosinfo
sdesc: "GObject based library API for managing information about OS, hypervisors and the (virtual) hardware devices (development)"
ldesc: "libosinfo is a GObject based library API for managing information about
operating systems, hypervisors and the (virtual) hardware devices they can
support. It includes a database containing device metadata and provides APIs
to match/identify optimal devices for deploying an operating system on a
hypervisor."
